body.p: During the past few days, twenty-nine real estate transfers have taken place in Chicago, in which the buyer, the seller, or both, were Scandinavian, as follows:

M. Thornberg to Nels Anderson, Princeton Avenue, north of 119th Street. Price $3,000.
